headline.main: CHINESE HALT PUSH IN HUNAN RICE AREA; Japanese Two-Pronged Drive Is Believed Another Effort to Seize Farming Belt

lead_paragraph: CHUNGKING, China, Nov. 1 (AP) -- Japanese forces attempting a new two-pronged drive from above Tungting Lake, apparently in another effort to conquer China's Hunan Province "rice bowl," have been checked or thrown back although fierce fighting is still raging, the Chinese High Command announced tonight.
